{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"alias":"turf-purple-dot","description":"## Reproduction Steps\n1. Run `rebar review-plan f93a-b947-558b-469c --output json` (a story with a ~2.6KB plan).\n2. Observe the returned coverage.metrics + verdict.\n\nObserved across 3 consecutive runs (attempts 3/4/5 in this session; cache cleared before attempt 5):\n\nExpected: Pass-2 verify dispatches over the Pass-1 findings (verify_requests > 0), findings are\nverified/decided, verdict is PASS or BLOCK. (This is what attempt 1 on an earlier revision of the same\nticket did: verify_requests=43, llm_ms=553581, verdict BLOCK with a verified finding.)\n\nActual: verdict INDETERMINATE with verify_requests=0, llm_ms~=21ms despite llm_calls=26, total_ms~=16s,\n0x HTTP 429, and a COMPLETELY EMPTY stderr (no warning/error/exception logged). All 17 Pass-1 findings\nfall through to `indeterminate` with reason `no-verification` because Pass-2 never dispatched. The result\nis deterministically reproducible on this ticket's current plan; clearing `.rebar/cache` (which had no\nentry for this ticket anyway) did not change it.\n\n## Why it matters\nA silent Pass-2 non-dispatch means the gate can return INDETERMINATE (fail-closed / non-signing) for a\nplan that has no blocking issue, with NO diagnostic in stderr — indistinguishable to an operator from a\nhealthy review. It also blocks earning a fresh attestation after a material edit. The llm_ms~=21ms /\nllm_calls=26 mismatch suggests Pass-1 was served from a cache (Anthropic prompt cache or other) and a\nfully-cached Pass-1 may be the trigger for Pass-2 being skipped — needs root-causing.\n\n## Context\nSurfaced while re-reviewing story f93a (eval-foundation, epic sure-foyer-aroma ac1b) after remediating a\nlegitimate BLOCK. Evidence JSONs: ~/.claude/jobs/19885ca3/tmp/planrev/f93a_rereview{,3,4,5}.json\n(attempt 1 = healthy verify; 3/4/5 = degraded). rebar 0.5.2 (c12ad713b-dirty).\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Root-cause why Pass-2 verify reports verify_requests=0 (llm_ms~=21ms, llm_calls=26) reproducibly on\n      this plan while attempt 1 verified normally; confirm/deny the cached-Pass-1 trigger hypothesis.\n- [ ] A degraded/skipped verify pass emits a diagnostic (stderr log + a coverage note) — never silent.\n- [ ] Either the gate re-dispatches verify on a cached Pass-1, or documents+justifies skipping it.\n- [ ] A regression test covers the cached-Pass-1 -> verify path so this cannot silently recur.","id":"4a4c-6fb2-67c8-41d4","parent_id":"","priority":2,"tags":["code-review","reliability","plan-review-gate"],"ticket_type":"bug","title":"Plan-review Pass-2 verify silently non-dispatches (verify_requests=0) reproducibly, yielding INDETERMINATE with empty stderr"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783270758859384001,"uuid":"69b82030-cdb5-489d-b02b-a4aaec11fe28"}